    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（朝。俺が寮の居間に入ると、みんなが）\n（パソコンの周りに集まって、ニュースを見ていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The following morning‚ when I enter the living room‚ all the girls)\n(are gathered around the computer‚ looking at the news.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.366666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい。トレンドに入ってますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look at that. We’re in the Trending tab.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.797256088256836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……『NEXT VENUSグランプリ』\n……『川咲さくら』……『長瀬麻奈』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“NEXT VENUS Grand Prix”…\n“Sakura Kawasaki”… “Mana Nagase”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.115850305557256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "私は？　私達の名前は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about me? Where’s my name?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.227823162078856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん。すずちゃん達月のテンペストの出番は\n一昨日だったからね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ well‚ Moon Tempest performed\nyesterday‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.032018264134717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "それよりこの記事は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind that. What’s this article about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.26535159746805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと……『NEXT VENUSグランプリ\n優勝するグループはズバリ！』……だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see… It says‚ “The NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚\nthis group has it in the bag!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.53634928067524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "『開催前は、満を持して臨むLizNoir、そして\n同じ事務所で人気を二分するTRINITYAiLE』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Before the event started‚ LizNoir was the long-awaited favorite‚ along with\nTRINITYAiLE‚ a group from the same agency.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.42802770932515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "『そのどちらかが優勝を争うと見られていたが\nここにきて俄然、混戦の様相を呈してきた……』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“It was speculated that one of those two groups would win‚\nbut suddenly‚ we appear to be in the middle of a fierce melee.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.38285752932228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "『これら二つのグループと遜色のない点数を叩き出した\nレジェンド長瀬麻奈の妹が所属する月のテンペスト』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Pounding out a score in no way inferior to these two groups\nwas Moon Tempest‚ a group led by Mana Nagase’s younger sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.65981888771052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "わあ……琴乃ちゃん、私達だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh‚ Kotono! That’s us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.30136062304175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.25136071840917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "『そして、長瀬麻奈の再来と言われる声を持つ\n川咲さくらを中心としたサニーピース』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“And Sunny Peace‚ a group led by Sakura Kawasaki‚\na singer said to be Mana Nagase’s second coming.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.45136071840916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4619271755218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "私達もいる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re in the article‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.51192717552179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "当然よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course we are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.11385462284082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "これって、つまり芽衣達も優勝候補ってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Does this mean we’re also considered favorites to win?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8341947436332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことになりますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed it does!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.51419485807412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ベスト8に残っている以上\n当然、そうなります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we’ve all made it into the Top 8‚\nof course we’re favorites.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.94752823909111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "この八グループから優勝が決まるんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The winner’s gonna be chosen from these eight groups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.19743751287449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "………………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.66045335531223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら\n……少しだけ話があるんだけど……いい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura.\nI need to talk to you for a bit. Got a minute?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.92712002197888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？\nうん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nMe too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1353512803712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……二人とも、練習は十時からよ\nそれまでに終わらせてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Practice starts at 10:00 sharp‚ you two.\nFinish it up by then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.07963695923468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "うん。分かってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We will.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.21297029256796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 121.37963695923467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それより朝食は？　お腹ペコペコですわよ\n当番は誰ですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind that‚ what about breakfast? I am starving.\nWhose turn is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.87718801101022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……\n……すずちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm…\nSuzu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "え…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.78725604613595,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5746.07728719738,
          "startTime": 138.53333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（みんながすずを睨む中、さくらと琴乃は居間を出た）\n（二人が気になる俺も、その後を追った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(While everyone turns to glare at Suzu‚ Sakura and Kotono leave the living room.)\n(I follow after them‚ curious to know what’s going on.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.75392271280282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_corridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 142.8872560461363
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 143.1539227128029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……\nもし嫌だったら、嫌って言ってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura…\nIf you don’t want to do it‚ just say so.",
